    <text id="B0421T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>James Hite records the statement of John McChesney regarding the care he gave to
                    an injured soldier, A. B. Sherer.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        
                        <name type="place">Newport, Augusta <abbr expan="County">Co.</abbr>
                            <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr><lb/>P.O. Moffat's Creek</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute/>
                </opener>

                <p>A.B. Sherer <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> to John McChesney</p>

                <p>June the 11 Two visits &amp; meds introducing <unclear>'batheter
                    twist</unclear> and dressing wound $8.00</p>

                <p>12 &amp; 13 Two visits and dressing wound and medicines 6.00</p>

                <p>14 16 &amp; 19 Three visits and dressing wound and <abbr expan="medicines"
                        >meds</abbr> 9.00</p>

                <p>21 26 &amp; 28 Three visits and <abbr expan="medicines">meds</abbr> dressing
                    wound 9.00</p>

                <p>29 Visit meds <abbr expan="extracting">ext</abbr> the bullet and dressing wound
                    5.00</p>

                <p>$37.00</p>

                <p>Augusta <abbr expan="County">Cty</abbr> Viz: This day doth John McChesney
                    personally appeared before me a magistrate for said <abbr expan="county"
                    >cty</abbr> and made oath to the above amount given under my honor this 20th day
                    of June 1867.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute/>
                    <signed>James F. Hite, <abbr expan="Justice of the Peace">J P</abbr></signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
